{"pageContext":{"notebook":"Dev","section":"Docker","page":{"id":"0-cdabcefafc54fb408df6e778abe4ebfb!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2141","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-cdabcefafc54fb408df6e778abe4ebfb!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2141","createdTime":"2018-12-22T12:18:08.696Z","title":"Docker-compose","createdByAppId":"","links":{"oneNoteEmbedUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!1937&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28Docker.one%7Cc134cdbf-f311-3945-bbdb-f8eecc1a6d52%2FDocker-compose%7C2a2b7a79-329d-f949-9f23-9391e38a1c06%2F%29"},"oneNoteClientUrl":{"href":"onenote:https://d.docs.live.net/bc575ab8e2ab9833/Documents/Dev/Docker.one#Docker-compose&section-id=c134cdbf-f311-3945-bbdb-f8eecc1a6d52&page-id=2a2b7a79-329d-f949-9f23-9391e38a1c06&end"},"oneNoteWebUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!1937&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28Docker.one%7Cc134cdbf-f311-3945-bbdb-f8eecc1a6d52%2FDocker-compose%7C2a2b7a79-329d-f949-9f23-9391e38a1c06%2F%29"}},"contentUrl":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-cdabcefafc54fb408df6e778abe4ebfb!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2141/content","lastModifiedTime":"2018-12-22T12:57:43Z","parentSection@odata.context":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/$metadata#me/notes/sections('0-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212141')/pages('0-cdabcefafc54fb408df6e778abe4ebfb%211-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212141')/parentSection(id,name,self)/$entity","parentSection":{"id":"0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2141","name":"Docker","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/sections/0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2141"},"content":"       yml파일로 docker container명세를 정의하는 것.    특정 프로젝트 폴더 안에서 docker.compose.yml 파일을 만들어서 정의한 후,    docker-compose up 으로 Docker container를 생성 및 실행 가능하다            docker-compose down -v --rmi all --remove-orphans    설명    모든 이미지와 컨테이너 지우기    옵션        --rmi type                  Remove images. Type must be one of:                                  'all': Remove all images used by any service.                                  'local': Remove only images that don't have a                                  custom tag set by the `image` field.        -v, --volumes               Remove named volumes declared in the `volumes`                                section of the Compose file and anonymous volumes                                attached to containers.        --remove-orphans            Remove containers for services not defined in the Compose file           ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:48px;top:115px;width:576px\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">yml<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD30C;&#xC77C;&#xB85C;</span> docker container<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBA85;&#xC138;&#xB97C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC815;&#xC758;&#xD558;&#xB294;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC83;</span>.</p>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD2B9;&#xC815;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD504;&#xB85C;&#xC81D;&#xD2B8;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD3F4;&#xB354;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC548;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C;</span> docker.compose.yml <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD30C;&#xC77C;&#xC744;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB9CC;&#xB4E4;&#xC5B4;&#xC11C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC815;&#xC758;&#xD55C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD6C4;</span>,</p>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:lime;font-weight:bold\">docker-compose up</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> &#xC73C;&#xB85C;</span> Docker container<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB97C; &#xC0DD;&#xC131; &#xBC0F; &#xC2E4;&#xD589; &#xAC00;&#xB2A5;&#xD558;&#xB2E4;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" data-tag=\"remember-for-later\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;font-size:10.5pt;color:teal\">docker</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">-compose down -v --rmi </span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas;font-size:10.5pt;color:#333333\">all</span><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\"> --remove-orphans</span></p>\n\t\t\t<h3 style=\"color:#5b9bd5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC124;&#xBA85;</span></h3>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBAA8;&#xB4E0; &#xC774;&#xBBF8;&#xC9C0;&#xC640; &#xCEE8;&#xD14C;&#xC774;&#xB108; &#xC9C0;&#xC6B0;&#xAE30;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<h3 lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"color:#5b9bd5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC635;&#xC158;</span></h3>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">    --rmi type</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">              Remove images. Type must be one of:</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">                              &apos;all&apos;: Remove all images used by any service.</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">                              &apos;local&apos;: Remove only images that don&apos;t have a</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">                              custom tag set by the `image` field.</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">    -v, --volumes</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">           Remove named volumes declared in the `volumes`</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">                            section of the Compose file and anonymous volumes</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">                            attached to containers.</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">    --remove-orphans</p>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">        Remove containers for services not defined in the Compose file</p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\n"}}}